  "description": "<p><strong>据国外媒体报道，激光原子钟将很快改变我们测量时间的方式。国外一组以&#160;Jerome&#160;Lodewyck&#160;科学家为首的巴黎天文台物理学家已经成功使用激 光原子钟将&#160;3&#160;亿年的时间差精确到一秒之内，</strong>拥有这种精确度的原子时钟可以重新定义“秒”，可角逐新一代国际标准原子钟的地位，希望能成为新的全球计时 标准。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e79aa0a/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244211.htm&amp;t=%E6%BF%80%E5%85%89%E5%8E%9F%E5%AD%90%E9%92%9F%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E6%96%B0%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E8%AE%A1%E6%97%B6%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244211.htm&amp;t=%E6%BF%80%E5%85%89%E5%8E%9F%E5%AD%90%E9%92%9F%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E6%96%B0%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E8%AE%A1%E6%97%B6%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244211.htm&amp;t=%E6%BF%80%E5%85%89%E5%8E%9F%E5%AD%90%E9%92%9F%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E6%96%B0%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E8%AE%A1%E6%97%B6%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244211.htm&amp;t=%E6%BF%80%E5%85%89%E5%8E%9F%E5%AD%90%E9%92%9F%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E6%96%B0%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E8%AE%A1%E6%97%B6%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244211.htm&amp;t=%E6%BF%80%E5%85%89%E5%8